emuInput.TitMainTitle: Group portrait of FROGS wives, including Ann Barnett, Miriam Sharp Fountain, Ms. Washington, Louise Ford, Helen Shield, and Marilyn Fountain, with Morris Fountain [blurred] near front, posed in Redwood Motor Hotel for FROGS Dinner - Dance party
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 10, 1970, pg. 15, reads: "Frogs Dinner - Dancing Party Sparks Holiday Season - The FROGS Played host to one of that smartest and gayest parties of the holiday at the Redwood Motor Hotel. The affair was in honor of their wives, some of whom are pictured here. All Courier Photos by 'Teenie' Harris."
